Class AfterTimeOnlyPredicate

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.navis.framework.portal.query.AbstractFieldPredicate
      • com.navis.framework.portal.query.SimplePredicate
        • com.navis.framework.portal.query.AfterTimeOnlyPredicate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MetaFilter, PredicateIntf, java.io.Serializable, java.util.function.Predicate<ValueHolder>

    public class AfterTimeOnlyPredicate
extends SimplePredicate
    Created with IntelliJ IDEA. User: ignatan Date: 8/15/13 Time: 8:18 AM This class is predicate for selecting objects where Datetime field is greater than a spesific time (with stripped date). This predicate is helpful when we have to select all objects for a working shift. The granularity is one second.
